field.description:
More than one email can be used, separate them with the comma. To specify the email subject use the colon character Example: 'test@yahoo.com:Thank you for participation'

						Also you may use the field value from the saved or added record using Twig tags.

						Example 1: {{ email }}
						Example 2: test@yahoo.com,test@gmail.com, {{ email }}
						Example 3: {{ customeremail }}:Thank you {{ name }} for participation
